]: Reference the female in the uploaded photo, changing into K-pop stage style clothing. Upper body features an off-white hollow-out knitted cropped long-sleeve cover-up, worn over a nude tube top, paired with high-waisted retro blue denim shorts with leopard print fur trim, and a dark leather belt hanging a brown heart-shaped plush charm. Temperament is gentle yet powerful, facial features are exquisite and clear, face is stable without deformation, maintaining same character consistency. [
  Action
]: One-take continuous dance, professional choreography quality. Starts with feet standing shoulder-width apart, core always tight. First beat: Right foot takes a large step sideways, center of gravity pressed low, while right hand "chops" diagonally down from the top of the head, left hand rests on hip, head snaps following the right hand's direction; Second beat: Quickly retract right foot, hips do a figure-8 circle, hands cross in front of chest then "explode" open to both sides; Third beat: Left foot steps back, body leans back doing a body wave, hands "comb" hair back from the top of the head; Fourth beat: Center of gravity shifts forward into a lunge, right hand "points" forward at the lens, left hand pulls back, creating diagonal tension. Throughout the movement, there is a sense of extension, fingertips and toes have direction, it is not soft and floppy swinging. [
  Scene
]: Fashionable and simple indoor stage background, warm side light outlines body lines, ground has slight mirror reflection, cinematic depth of field blurring the background. [
  Camera Movement
]: Medium shot, Smooth Orbit slowly circles around the subject, keeping the character always in the center of the frame, simulating a professional stage direct shot. [
  Style/Quality
]: 4K Ultra HD, cinematic texture, eliminate reshoot noise, sharpness clear, rich details, colors natural and realistic, no flickering, movements smooth without frame drops. [
  Constraints
]: Normal human body structure, movements have points of force application and extension, facial features highly restore the original photo, image stable and smooth, movements forbidden to look like posing or doing radio calisthenics.

